# Task Checklist

## Initialization
- [ ] Read and understand TASK.yml
- [ ] Review linked context files
- [ ] Clarify any ambiguities
- [ ] Create state/progress.yml

## Execution
- [ ] Begin task work
- [ ] Update progress regularly
- [ ] Create artifacts as needed
- [ ] Handle any errors gracefully

## Finalization
- [ ] Write RESULT.md
- [ ] Write RETURN.md
- [ ] Verify success criteria met
- [ ] Update INSTANCE.yml status

## On Abandonment
- [ ] Write postmortem to RESULT.md
- [ ] Note partial progress
- [ ] Document failure reason
- [ ] Mark status as "abandoned"

